64. **[^](#cite_ref-rfc2874_72-0)** M. Crawford; C. Huitema (July 2000). [*DNS Extensions to Support IPv6 Address Aggregation and Renumbering*](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc2874). Network Working Group. [doi](/wiki/Doi_(identifier) "Doi (identifier)"):[10.17487/RFC2874](https://doi.org/10.17487%2FRFC2874). [RFC](/wiki/Request_for_Comments "Request for Comments") [2874](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc2874). *Historic.* Updated by RFC [3152](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc3152), [3226](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc3226), [3363](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc3363) and [3364](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc3364). Updates RFC [1886](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc1886).
65. **[^](#cite_ref-73)** [Comparison of AAAA and A6 (do we really need A6?)](https://tools.ietf.org/html/draft-ietf-dnsext-aaaa-a6-01), Jun-ichiro itojun Hagino, (July 2001)
66. ^ [***a***](#cite_ref-rfc3363_74-0) [***b***](#cite_ref-rfc3363_74-1) R. Bush; A. Durand; B. Fink; O. Gudmundsson; T. Hain, eds. (August 2002). [*Representing Internet Protocol version 6 (IPv6) Addresses in the Domain Name System (DNS)*](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc3363). Network Working Group. [doi](/wiki/Doi_(identifier) "Doi (identifier)"):[10.17487/RFC3363](https://doi.org/10.17487%2FRFC3363). [RFC](/wiki/Request_for_Comments "Request for Comments") [3363](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc3363). *Informational.* Updates RFC [2673](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc2673), [2874](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc2874).
67. **[^](#cite_ref-rfc3364_75-0)** R. Austein (August 2002). [*Tradeoffs in Domain Name System (DNS) Support for Internet Protocol version 6 (IPv6)*](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc3364). Network Working Group. [doi](/wiki/Doi_(identifier) "Doi (identifier)"):[10.17487/RFC3364](https://doi.org/10.17487%2FRFC3364). [RFC](/wiki/Request_for_Comments "Request for Comments") [3364](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc3364). *Informational.* Updates RFC [2673](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc2673), [2874](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc2874).
68. ^ [***a***](#cite_ref-rfc6536_76-0) [***b***](#cite_ref-rfc6536_76-1) A. Bierman; M. Bjorklund (March 2012). [*Network Configuration Protocol (NETCONF) Access Control Model*](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc6536). [Internet Engineering Task Force](/wiki/Internet_Engineering_Task_Force "Internet Engineering Task Force"). [doi](/wiki/Doi_(identifier) "Doi (identifier)"):[10.17487/RFC6536](https://doi.org/10.17487%2FRFC6536). [RFC](/wiki/Request_for_Comments "Request for Comments") [6536](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc6536). *Obsolete.* Obsoleted by [RFC](/wiki/RFC_(identifier) "RFC (identifier)") [8341](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc8341).
